Bring the ancient tomes to Candúr
Bring the ancient tomes to Candúr.

A wealth of lore awaits those who brave the Bones of Barad-dûr.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Barad-dûr: Realm of the Black Word to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
'These rare texts should be studied by the Lore-masters of Minas Tirith. I will give these tomes to Isnír for study.'
